[[Thumbnail(manhole.jpg, 230, "A manhole by ["Sharps and Flats"].")]]

Until now, citizens of Davis had to stumble helplessly through the streets in search of manholes.  The City and various corporations attempt to limit information on this important topic.  In the interest of the public good, we press on with a critical analysis of Davis' vast and often chaotic '''["Manholes" Manhole and Manhole cover system]'''.
